overview: A digital video for Stand-Up Comedy Special entitled Komoidoumenoi by Pandji Pragiwaksono. The digital video consists of crowdwork, material regarding the apology to Mr. Hajj, a new party is not a solution, Pandji is reprimanded for death and many other materials. This video is uncensored, uncut, with an epilogue, 3 hours long.
title: Komoidoumenoi
